Package: dsHPCClient
Type: Package
Title: Observability and Administration for dsHPC
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Sarrat González", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "david.sarrat@isglobal.org"),
    person("Juan R", "González", role = "aut", email = "juanr.gonzalez@isglobal.org"))
Author: David Sarrat González [aut, cre],
    Juan R González [aut]
Maintainer: David Sarrat González <david.sarrat@isglobal.org>
Description: Client-side R package providing analysts with a cross-domain
    view of the dsHPC durable job queue (status, listing, scheduler
    observability, Studio dashboard) plus admin-key-gated destructive
    operations. Submission, output loading and pipeline composition are
    server-side concerns; domain packages such as dsImagingClient expose their
    own analyst-facing workflows that invoke domain DataSHIELD methods, which
    in turn use dsHPC server-side via R-internal calls.
